contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.blogpos.BlogPostContentContentMarkdown:
The Milwaukee Kentico User Group is taking off again and everyone's invited to join their next virtual event [Kentico Connection 2023 Conference Recap with Sean Wright](https://www.meetup.com/mkekug/events/297070910/).
Here's the agenda:
- Welcome all - Kentico's new community portal with Sean Wright - Conference highlights - Open discussion on community Kentico use
This event will be held online through Zoom on Wednesday, November 8, 2023 at 2:00 PM to 3:00 PM EST.
Come join the discussion or just listen in!
